entry.title: Ready for 0.3.23 release?
entry.summary: Jeff Garzik, a member of exMULTI, Inc. has sent out an email stating that Version 0.3.23 is free of any major issues and testing has been unremarkable. He suggests that the team can go ahead and push it out. In the email, he also asks for an ACK for the final release of Version 0.3.23. The email was cc'd to the developers who are not yet on the dev mailing list.
